Pop-on captions,
pop on and off the screen.

00:00:03.067,00:00:06.100
They are used with programs
with multiple characters.

00:00:06.100,00:00:08.467
They can be
strategically placed

00:00:08.467,00:00:11.167
as to indicate to the viewer
who is speaking.

00:00:11.167,00:00:12.400
For example,

00:00:12.400,00:00:13.633
if the person
is on the left side

00:00:13.633,00:00:14.733
of the screen

00:00:14.733,00:00:16.033
the pop-on captions
would appear

00:00:16.033,00:00:17.600
on the left side.

00:00:17.600,00:00:18.967
If they are
in the middle,

00:00:18.967,00:00:20.767
the caption would appear
in the middle.

00:00:20.767,00:00:22.333
Or, if they are on
the right side

00:00:22.333,00:00:23.567
of the screen

00:00:23.567,00:00:25.533
caption would pop-on
the right side.

